Response:
1. Increase app pool memory reservation.
2. Stagger export concurrency.
3. Apply CHG0004007 for permanent fix.', 'application', '["erp", "export", "memory"]'::jsonb, 'published', 'technician', 'USR00014', '2026-04-03T09:00:00Z'::timestamptz, '2026-04-03T09:00:00Z'::timestamptz, 67, 21, '["CI0000012"]'::jsonb, '["INC0001014", "INC0001025"]'::jsonb);
INSERT INTO "kb_knowledge" ("tenant_id", "kb_id", "title", "summary", "content", "category", "tags", "state", "audience", "created_by", "created_at", "updated_at", "views", "helpful_votes", "related_ci_ids", "related_incidents") VALUES ('T001', 'KB0005013', 'Change calendar outage fallback', 'Use API endpoint for calendar data while UI recovers.', 'When the change calendar UI returns 503:
1. Use the /api/v2/calendar endpoint directly.
2. Filter by date range.
3. Notify GRP-APPS to investigate.', 'itsm', '["change", "calendar"]'::jsonb, 'published', 'technician', 'USR00005', '2026-04-03T10:00:00Z'::timestamptz, '2026-04-03T10:00:00Z'::timestamptz, 41, 13, '["CI0000013"]'::jsonb, '["INC0001015"]'::jsonb);
