Fix:
1. Generate new certs from internal CA.
2. Replace cert files on probe host.
3. Restart probe agent service.
4. Verify discovery resumes.', 'cmdb', '["cmdb", "discovery", "certificate"]'::jsonb, 'published', 'technician', 'USR00015', '2026-04-03T11:00:00Z'::timestamptz, '2026-04-03T11:00:00Z'::timestamptz, 38, 11, '["CI0000014"]'::jsonb, '["INC0001016", "INC0001026"]'::jsonb);
