1. Lower the age boost weight in the rank profile.
2. Increase semantic relevance weight.
3. Retrain on recent feedback.
4. Validate top-5 results for known queries.', 'knowledge', '["kb", "search", "ranking"]'::jsonb, 'published', 'technician', 'USR00017', '2026-04-03T12:00:00Z'::timestamptz, '2026-04-03T12:00:00Z'::timestamptz, 22, 9, '["CI0000015"]'::jsonb, '["INC0001017", "INC0001028"]'::jsonb);
